Multiplying synergies with players in the housing chain, ICF Habitat acts for the economic, social and sustainable development of territories:

• increase in rental supply with the production of 1,500 to 2,000 housing units each year, in areas with high needs;

• proposal of a housing offer adapted to the needs and resources of all audiences;

