To establish its development, ICF Habitat relies on the know-how and capacity for innovation of its 1,521 employees. The Group is therefore deploying an ambitious HR policy to attract and develop talent, focusing on promoting collective performance as much as individual potential, providing training and development opportunities throughout the career path and meeting expectations. and the ambitions of its employees. In a sector undergoing profound change, ICF Habitat ensures the development of new skills in order to support the evolution of professions and the digitalization of activities. A responsible employer, ICF Habitat defends the principles of openness, dialogue and diversity which constitute its DNA.

